text: Antoinette Kuiters (born 11 September 1939) is a South African gymnast. She competed in five events at the 1960 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1939 births Category:Living people Category:South African female artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of South Africa Category:Gymnasts at the 1960 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Schiedam
